Package: shigella
Title: Shigella Antibody-Kinetics Analysis and Reporting Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9009
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kwan Ho", "Lee", , "ksjlee@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Douglas Ezra", "Morrison", , "demorrison@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7195-830X")))
Description: Reproducible analysis tools for fitting and evaluating Bayesian
    two-phase decay models of Shigella antibody kinetics from longitudinal
    serosurvey data. Provides functions for posterior prediction, model
    comparison, sensitivity analysis, and publication-ready tables and figures
    supporting serosurveillance applications.
